2026-05-09T19:26:21.5940191Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5941036Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5941820Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5942756Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5943770Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5944689Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5945617Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5946485Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5949403Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5950415Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5951172Z 33    -->
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5951878Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5953003Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5954355Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5955516Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
