2026-05-09T19:26:21.5963121Z 38        Used on Samsung and other OEM devices that aggressively optimize
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5964204Z 39        battery usage. MainActivity shows a one-time dialog that opens
2026-05-09T19:26:21.5965155Z 40        the system "ignore battery optimizations" screen so scheduled
